tps://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1692078075","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":59673,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","stars":8693,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":482311,"username":"shuaishuaivip","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shuaishuaivip","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1eb0bc29667210a78d84bdbf91a165f5?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1eb0bc29667210a78d84bdbf91a165f5?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1eb0bc29667210a78d84bdbf91a165f5?s=73&d=retro","created":1586310754,"last_modified":1698633206},"last_reply_by":"tmdbbr","last_touched":1698634571,"title":"程序员一般用什么洗发水来防止脱发？推荐下～","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/986604","created":1698633214,"deleted":0,"content":"程序员，一般熬夜，油性发质，几乎天天要洗头不洗头就觉得脑袋很重，但是天天洗头对头发又不好。请问你们用傻子牌的洗发水，来预防脱发哦～","content_rendered":"程序员，一般熬夜，油性发质，几乎天天要洗头不洗头就觉得脑袋很重，但是天天洗头对头发又不好。请问你们用傻子牌的洗发水，来预防脱发哦～","last_modified":1698633214,"replies":23,"id":986604},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655","name":"hardware","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655","title":"硬件","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","topics":5308,"footer":"","header":"硬件发烧友的讨论节点","title_alternative":"Hardware","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","stars":2326,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":52,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":560835,"username":"Arch3r","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Arch3r","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5513fb5a2b22e1f8bdc9dbef5ee8bea9?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5513fb5a2b22e1f8bdc9dbef5ee8bea9?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5513fb5a2b22e1f8bdc9dbef5ee8bea9?s=73&d=retro","created":1636103460,"last_modified":1698627185},"last_reply_by":"Arch3r","last_touched":1698633690,"title":"mac 外接显示器 dell u2723qe vs 优派 vg2481","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/986562","created":1698628394,"deleted":0,"content":"## Dell u2723qe\r\n27 寸 4K 3189\r\n优点：\r\n支持 KVM ，可以接两个输入源，支持画中画，画旁画。\r\n\r\n\r\n## 优派 vg2481\r\n24 寸 4K 1999\r\n优点：\r\nPPI 更高，并且接 mac 缩放效果更好，便宜\r\n\r\n## 需求\r\n现在就是需要接 macbook ，和一个 windows 笔记本，有时需要同时显示 mac 和 windows 的内容。目前想有两种方式：\r\n1. mac 连接 windows 的远程桌面，现在就是这种方式，感觉还可以。（这样就买啥显示器都行）\r\n2. 买 dell 的显示器支持 KVM 画旁画，左右分屏。\r\n\r\n## 现在纠结的点\r\n1. 我的桌面纵深 50cm ，27 寸的是不是太大了。\r\n2. 用远程桌面确实稍微有点延迟，是不是用 KVM 的分屏，体验好些。就是不知道 dell 的分屏用起来实际体验怎么样。\r\n3. 有没有办法一根 type-c 连接显示器的时候，只用来传输数据，不用它充电。担心烧主板。\r\n4. 需要同时显示 mac 和 windows 的时间并不是很多。","content_rendered":"<h2>Dell u2723qe</h2>\n<p>27 寸 4K 3189\n优点：\n支持 KVM ，可以接两个输入源，支持画中画，画旁画。</p>\n<h2>优派 vg2481</h2>\n<p>24 寸 4K 1999\n优点：\nPPI 更高，并且接 mac 缩放效果更好，便宜</p>\n<h2>需求</h2>\n<p>现在就是需要接 macbook ，和一个 windows 笔记本，有时需要同时显示 mac 和 windows 的内容。目前想有两种方式：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>mac 连接 windows 的远程桌面，现在就是这种方式，感觉还可以。（这样就买啥显示器都行）</li>\n<li>买 dell 的显示器支持 KVM 画旁画，左右分屏。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>现在纠结的点</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>我的桌面纵深 50cm ，27 寸的是不是太大了。</li>\n<li>用远程桌面确实稍微有点延迟，是不是用 KVM 的分屏，体验好些。就是不知道 dell 的分屏用起来实际体验怎么样。</li>\n<li>有没有办法一根 type-c 连接显示器的时候，只用来传输数据，不用它充电。担心烧主板。</li>\n<li>需要同时显示 mac 和 windows 的时间并不是很多。</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1698629370,"replies":20,"id":986562},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2e